entities.LylyraHelper/DashActivatedDustBunnies/Rotate.placements.name.main=Dash Activated Dust Bunny (Rotate)
entities.LylyraHelper/DashActivatedDustBunnies/Rotate.placements.description.main=A Dust Bunny that rotates by a specified angle whenever the player dashes.
entities.LylyraHelper/DashActivatedDustBunny.placements.name.main=Dash Activated Dust Bunny
entities.LylyraHelper/DashActivatedDustBunny.placements.description.main=A Dust Bunny that moves to its next node whenever the player dashes.
entities.LylyraHelper/DashActivatedDustBunny.attributes.description.TravelTime=The time taken to move to the next location.
